[SN]TITLE[SN]
One dead in Isle of Lewis road crash

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
One person has died after a crash on the Barvas to Carloway road on the Isle of Lewis.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
Emergency services were called to a serious accident on the A858, close to the road's junction to Brue, at about 13:30 on Saturday.
Details of the victim of the crash are yet to be released.
Police Scotland closed the road in both directions for several hours while crash investigations took place. It has now reopened.
